  <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
  <div class="first">
    Your privacy is important to BUBBLE and always has been.
    So we’ve developed a Privacy Policy that covers how we use and store your information.
    Please take a moment to familiarize yourself with our privacy practices
    and let us know if you have any questions.
