    or social networking service,
    the personal information and content you share is visible to other users and can be read,
    collected, or used by them.
    You are responsible for the personal information you choose to share or submit in these instances.
    For example, if you list your BUBBLE ID and email address in a forum posting,
    that information is public. Please take care when using these features.
  </div>
  <div class="first">
    We may decline to process requests that are frivolous/vexatious,
