      to BUBBLE employees and strictly enforce privacy safeguards within the company.
    </div>
  </div>
  <h3>Privacy Questions</h3>
  <div class="first">
    If you have any questions or concerns about BUBBLE’s Privacy Policy
    or data processing or if you would like to make a complaint about a possible breach of local privacy laws,
    please contact us.
    All such communications are examined and replies issued where appropriate as soon as possible.
  </div>
  <div class="first">
